WEBVTT

00:00:16.996 --> 00:00:21.375 line:90% position:50% align:center
Doubt and fear surround me—

00:00:21.375 --> 00:00:26.255 line:90% position:50% align:center
The way ahead not clear.

00:00:26.255 --> 00:00:31.427 line:90% position:50% align:center
Through uncertainty you guide me;

00:00:31.427 --> 00:00:36.807 line:90% position:50% align:center
I know you’re always near.

00:00:36.807 --> 00:00:41.312 line:90% position:50% align:center
Life may not be easy,

00:00:41.312 --> 00:00:46.442 line:90% position:50% align:center
But this I know is true:

00:00:46.442 --> 00:00:51.572 line:90% position:50% align:center
You’re the God who’s ever loyal;

00:00:51.572 --> 00:00:56.660 line:90% position:50% align:center
My life is safe with you.

00:00:56.660 --> 00:01:01.999 line:90% position:50% align:center
Jehovah, give me eyes of faith

00:01:01.999 --> 00:01:06.629 line:90% position:50% align:center
And help me always see

00:01:06.629 --> 00:01:11.717 line:90% position:50% align:center
There are more with us than against us.

00:01:11.717 --> 00:01:17.306 line:90% position:50% align:center
Courageous let me be.

00:01:17.306 --> 00:01:21.602 line:90% position:50% align:center
Courage, give me courage;

00:01:21.602 --> 00:01:27.024 line:90% position:50% align:center
With courage, I’ll endure.

00:01:27.024 --> 00:01:32.071 line:90% position:50% align:center
Jehovah, give me courage;

00:01:32.071 --> 00:01:38.160 line:90% position:50% align:center
Your victory is sure.

00:01:40.329 --> 00:01:44.708 line:90% position:50% align:center
Feeling fear is human.

00:01:44.708 --> 00:01:49.713 line:90% position:50% align:center
In my own strength, I’m frail.

00:01:49.713 --> 00:01:54.843 line:90% position:50% align:center
You have been my rock and refuge;

00:01:54.843 --> 00:02:00.182 line:90% position:50% align:center
Your power never fails.

00:02:00.182 --> 00:02:04.979 line:90% position:50% align:center
Help me be courageous,

00:02:04.979 --> 00:02:09.733 line:90% position:50% align:center
And let my heart be brave.

00:02:09.733 --> 00:02:14.905 line:90% position:50% align:center
Lasting harm can never hold me—

00:02:14.905 --> 00:02:20.077 line:90% position:50% align:center
No prison, gate, or grave.

00:02:20.077 --> 00:02:25.374 line:90% position:50% align:center
Jehovah, give me eyes of faith

