With courage, I’ll endure.

00:02:50.274 --> 00:02:56.905 line:90% position:50% align:center
Jehovah, give me courage;

00:02:56.905 --> 00:03:05.122 line:90% position:50% align:center
Your victory is sure.

00:03:13.881 --> 00:03:16.717 line:90% position:50% align:center
Look around us now;

00:03:16.717 --> 00:03:20.596 line:90% position:50% align:center
See the love on each face—

00:03:20.596 --> 00:03:27.352 line:90% position:50% align:center
Out there in the world, hard to find.

00:03:27.352 --> 00:03:30.606 line:90% position:50% align:center
All these faithful friends

00:03:30.606 --> 00:03:34.318 line:90% position:50% align:center
With the love they all show,

00:03:34.318 --> 00:03:39.615 line:90% position:50% align:center
Glad to leave that old world behind.

00:03:42.367 --> 00:03:46.622 line:90% position:50% align:center
Love never fails; that’s promised.

00:03:49.333 --> 00:03:54.797 line:90% position:50% align:center
It always will endure.

00:03:54.797 --> 00:03:59.927 line:90% position:50% align:center
Love—unfailing love—

00:03:59.927 --> 00:04:04.640 line:90% position:50% align:center
That’s what Jehovah gives.

00:04:04.640 --> 00:04:08.519 line:90% position:50% align:center
That’s what he is.

00:04:08.519 --> 00:04:13.816 line:90% position:50% align:center
Love—unfailing love—

00:04:13.816 --> 00:04:18.487 line:90% position:50% align:center
